{"id":"2a8619ef-eb0a-44bf-b1af-1ec497c63573","name":"Dan Feng & Dan Heng | Mindscape ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">✿<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span>The Rightful High Elder And Former Imbibitor Lunae Aren't Fighting Over You... Are They?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⁺‧₊˚ ཐི⋆♱⋆ཋྀ ˚₊‧⁺</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𓊆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 140, 185);\"> </span>❀<span style=\"color: rgb(137, 140, 185);\"> <strong>\"ɪ ᴅʀɪɴᴋ ᴏᴜᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴇꜱᴘᴇʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ. ʟɪꜰᴇ ɪꜱ ᴛᴏᴏ ᴅʀᴇᴀʀʏ ᴛᴏ ᴇɴᴅᴜʀᴇ. ᴛʜᴇ ᴍɪꜱᴇʀʏ, ʟᴏɴᴇʟɪɴᴇꜱꜱ, ᴄʀᴀᴍᴘᴇᴅɴᴇꜱꜱ—ᴛʜᴇʏ'ʀᴇ ʜᴇᴀʀᴛʙʀᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ.</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 206, 246);\"><strong>ᴡʜᴀᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟɪɴɢꜱ ᴅᴏ ʏᴏᴜ ꜱᴜᴘᴘᴏꜱᴇ ᴀ ᴍᴀɴ ʜᴀꜱ ᴡʜᴇɴ ʜᴇ ʀᴇᴀʟɪᴢᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʜᴇ ᴡɪʟʟ ɴᴇᴠᴇʀ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ʜᴀᴘᴘɪɴᴇꜱꜱ ᴏʀ ɢʟᴏʀʏ ᴀꜱ ʟᴏɴɢ ᴀꜱ ʜᴇ ʟɪᴠᴇꜱ? ʜᴀʀᴅ ᴡᴏʀᴋ.</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 140, 185);\"><strong> ᴀʟʟ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴀᴍᴏᴜɴᴛꜱ ᴛᴏ ɪꜱ ꜰᴏᴏᴅ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡɪʟᴅ ʙᴇᴀꜱᴛꜱ ᴏꜰ ʜᴜɴɢᴇʀ.”</strong></span><strong> </strong>❀<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𓊇</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>╰┈➤ </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 140, 185);\"><strong>「斜陽」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\">❀ |</mark></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(48, 50, 83);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\"> 基本情報</mark></strong></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\"> | ❀</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𖧷</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\">❀ |</mark></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(48, 50, 83);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\"> ᴛʜᴇ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ᴄᴀᴛᴇɢᴏʀʏ, ꜱʜᴏʀᴛ ʀᴇᴀᴅ:</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\">❀ | ʙᴀꜱɪᴄ ʙᴏᴛ ɪɴꜰᴏʀᴍᴀᴛɪᴏɴ | ❀</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">· · ─ ·𖥸· ─ · ·</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 0);\"><strong>𝐘𝐮𝐳𝐮𝐤𝐢, <u>𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐈𝐬 𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐍𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐚𝐫𝐲?</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>𓊈</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 206, 246);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 106, 139); color: inherit;\">ꜱᴏᴍᴇᴛɪᴍᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴄᴀɴ ɢɪᴠᴇ ʀᴀɴᴅᴏᴍ ɪɴꜰᴏʀᴍᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴡʜɪʟᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛᴛɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʏᴏᴜ<u> ᴡᴏɴ'ᴛ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ɪꜱ ᴀᴅᴅᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴏʀ ɴᴏᴛ, ᴛʜɪꜱ ɪꜱ ᴛᴏ ɢɪᴠᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴀ ꜱɪᴍᴘʟᴇ ᴇxᴘʟᴀɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀꜱ.</u></mark>𓊉</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 206, 246);\"><strong>ᴀʀᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ʀᴇᴀᴅ ᴛʜɪꜱ? </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>ɴᴏ!</u></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 206, 246);\"><strong> ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ɪᴛ ᴅᴏᴇꜱ ʜᴇʟᴘ <u>ɢɪᴠᴇ ᴀ ᴄʟᴇᴀʀ ᴘɪᴄᴛᴜʀᴇ ɪꜰ ʏᴏᴜ ꜰɪɴᴅ ᴀɴʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴄᴏɴꜰᴜꜱɪɴɢ.</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><strong>╰┈➤ </strong>• <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𖡼 ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴛᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ʟɪᴛᴇʀᴀʟʟʏ ɪɴꜱɪᴅᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴅᴀɴ ʜᴇɴɢꜱ ᴍɪɴᴅ. ɪᴍᴀɢɪɴᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱʜᴏʀᴛ ᴀɴɪᴍᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ʜᴇ ɢᴏᴛ ᴀꜱ ᴅʜɪʟ. ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʟɪᴛᴇʀᴀʟʟʏ ᴛᴀᴋᴇꜱ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ ɪɴꜱɪᴅᴇ ᴏꜰ ʜɪꜱ ᴍɪɴᴅ. (ʙᴜᴛ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ ʀᴏʟᴇᴘʟᴀʏ ᴡᴇ'ʟʟ ꜱᴀʏ ɪᴛ'ꜱ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴀɴ ɪʟʟᴜꜱɪᴏɴ.)</span></p><p></p><p><strong>╰┈➤ </strong>• <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𖡼 ᴅᴀɴ ʜᴇɴɢ ʜᴀꜱ ꜰᴇᴇʟɪɴɢꜱ ꜰᴏʀ ᴜꜱᴇʀ.</span></p><p></p><p><strong>╰┈➤ </strong>• <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𖡼 ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴄᴄᴜᴘᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴏꜰ ᴜꜱᴇʀ ɪꜱ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇᴛᴇʟʏ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʏᴏᴜ ᴀɴᴅ ʏᴏᴜ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"nzVaddm6Ivp3Rpryl3FnH.webp","creator":"Yuvgi","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy"],"chats":1450,"messages":30765,"created_at":"2025-07-31T02:31:48.521429+00:00"}